		<tooltip id="tt_11">
			<description>Choose the timestamp that will be added to the backup filenames.</description>
		</tooltip>
		<tooltip id="tt_13">
			<description>Comma separated list of URLs to override. If the currently loaded page is one of these URLs, the page will be opened on the current tab..</description>
		</tooltip>
		<tooltip id="tt_14">
			<description>Comma separated list of servers/host names to override. If the currently loaded page contains one of these servers/host names in its URL, the page will be opened on the current tab.</description>
		</tooltip>
		<tooltip id="tt_16">
			<description>If <html:b>enabled/checked</html:b>, the custom style sheet inside the Help tab of the button will be applied to the main menu.</description>
		</tooltip>
		<tooltip id="tt_17">
			<description>If <html:b>enabled/checked</html:b> and the current tab is any &quot;about:&quot; page, the tab will be overwrited. If <html:b>disabled/unchecked</html:b>, only tabs specified in the list of URLs/hosts will be overwrited.</description>
		</tooltip>
		<tooltip id="tt_18">
